<span class="line"><span style="color:#EBA0AC;font-style:italic;">    description</span><span style="color:#94E2D5;">=</span><span style="color:#A6E3A1;">&quot;Review the fix for correctness, security, and test coverage.&quot;</span><span style="color:#9399B2;">,</span></span>
